《'''明天別再來敲門'''》（{{lang-sv|''En man som heter Ove''}}）是一部瑞典[[剧情片|剧情片]]，2015年12月25日在瑞典上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sfi.se/sv/svensk-filmdatabas/Item/?itemid=79650&type=MOVIE&iv=Basic|title=En man som heter Ove|publisher=Swedish Film Database|language=sv|date=2015-12-25|accessdate=2016-09-30|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305015154/http://www.sfi.se/sv/svensk-filmdatabas/Item/?itemid=79650&type=MOVIE&iv=Basic|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由[[汉内斯·霍尔姆|汉内斯·霍尔姆]]执导和编剧，改编自作家[[弗雷德里克·贝克曼|弗雷德里克·贝克曼]]2012年的[[明天别再来敲门_(小说)|同名小说]]。主角欧维由[[罗尔夫·拉斯加德|罗尔夫·拉斯加德]]饰演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sfi.se/en-GB/Swedish-film-database/Item/?itemid=79650&type=MOVIE&iv=Basic|title=A Man Called Ove (2015)|publisher=Swedish Film Database|accessdate=2015-01-12|archive-date=2016-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160407224555/http://www.sfi.se/en-GB/Swedish-film-database/Item/?itemid=79650&type=MOVIE&iv=Basic|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影在[[金甲蟲獎|第51届金甲虫奖]]获得六个奖项提名，赢得最佳男主角和最佳化妆两个奖<ref name="2015nominees">{{cite press release|url=http://www.filminstitutet.se/en/about-us/press-service/press-archive/2016/nominations-for-the-2015-guldbagge-awards/|title=Nominations for the 2015 Guldbagge Awards|publisher=[[Swedish_Film_Institute|Swedish Film Institute]]|date=2016-01-04|access-date=2016-01-05|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304141543/http://www.filminstitutet.se/en/about-us/press-service/press-archive/2016/nominations-for-the-2015-guldbagge-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="51stGuldbaggeAwards">{{cite web|url=http://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/film/article22112062.ab|title=Glädjevrålet på Guldbaggegalan|first=Isabel|last=Norman|first2=Joni|last2=Nykänen|work=Aftonbladet|language=sv|date=2016-01-18|accessdate=2016-01-19|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617192709/https://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/film/article22112062.ab|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Sweden">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-sweden-selects-a-man-924938 |title=Oscars: Sweden Selects 'A Man Called Ove' for Foreign-Language Category |last=Roxborough |first=Scott |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2016-09-01 |accessdate=2016-09-01 |archive-date=2016-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011210805/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-sweden-selects-a-man-924938 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="DecSL">{{Cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/oscars-2017-foreign-language-race-1201943744/ |title=Oscars: Nine Films Advance in Foreign-Language Race |date=2016-12-15 |accessdate=2016-12-15 |work=Variety |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220184329/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/oscars-2017-foreign-language-race-1201943744/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。入围了[[第89屆奧斯卡金像獎|第89屆奧斯卡金像獎]][[奥斯卡最佳外语片|最佳外语片]]和[[奥斯卡最佳化妆与发型设计奖|最佳化妆与发型设计奖]]<ref name="expressen.se">{{cite web|url=http://www.expressen.se/noje/nu-kan-ove-vinna-ytterligare-en-oscar/|title="En man som heter Ove" kan få Oscar för make up och hår|work=Expressen|accessdate=2016-12-22|language=sv|archive-date=2019-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521165454/https://www.expressen.se/noje/nu-kan-ove-vinna-ytterligare-en-oscar/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Oscars2017">{{cite news |url=http://edit.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/oscar-nominations-2017-complete-list-nominees-960044 |title=Oscars: 'La La Land' Ties Record With 14 Nominations |first=Kimberly |last=Nordyke |publisher=''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]'' |date=January 24, 2017 |accessdate=January 24, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171202203454/http://edit.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/oscar-nominations-2017-complete-list-nominees-960044 |archive-date=2017-12-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="OscarsVar">{{cite news |url=http://variety.com/2017/film/news/2017-oscar-nominations-academy-awards-nominees-1201968107/ |title=Oscar Nominations: Complete List |publisher=''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]'' |date=January 24, 2017 |accessdate=January 24, 2017 |archive-date=2017-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170124150844/http://variety.com/2017/film/news/2017-oscar-nominations-academy-awards-nominees-1201968107/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==剧情==
最近丧偶、59岁的欧维（[[罗尔夫·拉斯加德|罗尔夫·拉斯加德]]饰演）给小镇邻居的印象是每天绷着脸和有自杀倾向。有一天，帕瓦内（[[巴哈·帕斯|巴哈·帕斯]]饰演）与其家人搬进了对面的房子，而他们的车撞掉了欧维的邮箱，这反而成为了这一段难以解释的友情的开始，阻止了欧维的自杀也掀开了他的对世界的温柔。

